Title: New endpoints for Best, Invited, Active, and Launches
Link: https://hnrss.github.io/#alternative-feeds
Description: <ul>
+ <li><a href="https://hnrss.org/best">https://hnrss.org/best</a> for the top recent vote getters</li>
+ <li><a href="https://hnrss.org/invited">https://hnrss.org/invited</a> for posts <a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=20508960">given a second chance by the mods</a></li>
+ <li><a href="https://hnrss.org/active">https://hnrss.org/active</a> for posts with active, ongoing discussions</li>
+ <li><a href="https://hnrss.org/launches">https://hnrss.org/launches</a> for YC launches</li>
+ </ul>
